{"tid":1372462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【光復元朗】《蘋果》直擊解放軍走出石崗軍營 穿戰鬥服荷槍巡邏","createTime":"2019-07-27T12:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T12:34:18.000Z","uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52d47446eda113a501e588b46ff6fc6806be7ebf","tid":1372462,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:25:06.000Z","msg":"//<br />\n警方下午於元朗大馬路一帶與市民發生衝突，不斷施放多枚催淚彈驅趕，甚至射到民居及西鐵路軌之中，與此同時，6公里外的石崗軍營亦重兵駐守，氣氛變得緊張。《蘋果》記者傍晚駕駛採訪車沿荃錦公路往錦田方向行駛，發現石崗軍營多個閘口外有解放軍駐守，人數較平日多，其間他們穿着戰鬥服，手持盾牌、衝鋒槍及鐵叉走出行人路巡邏。當他們見到本報的採訪車經過時，立即揮手命令記者不准停留，立即離開。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190727/59870393\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190727%2F59870393&d=IcHW%2FfQ2zQNJFdNzTrXWKBSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=815f02f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190727%2F59870393&h=aa32d5fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190727/59870393</a>"},{"pid":"ff14ccfeb30aeab58921b569dc3ddf1673203fa4","tid":1372462,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:26:22.000Z","msg":"唔係掛"},{"pid":"e73d91c50da40e0ca4a5cd473ed5aaf7ce56fba2","tid":1372462,"uid":172227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:27:18.000Z","msg":"做到出面了dllm"},{"pid":"43feb2481b89e7bda77064bb5b0408b607bda8c3","tid":1372462,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:30:22.000Z","msg":"快D出兵啦"},{"pid":"f1db972161e600cd6fb1b806274970dfc320a363","tid":1372462,"uid":249794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52d47446eda113a501e588b46ff6fc6806be7ebf","tid":1372462,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:25:06.000Z","msg":"//<br />\n警方下午於元朗大馬路一帶與